'''Tom O'Neill''' was an illustrator and graphic artist who worked on [[West End Games]] ''[[Star Wars: The Roleplaying Game]]'' sourcebooks. He served as an art director for ''[[Lords of the Expanse]]'' and ''[[Alien Encounters]]''.

